HOME - MESSAGE - FAQ - RULES- WANTED - NAVIGATION

Star Studded is a plotless celebrity group that is semi appless. Every person starts of with one secret that will be exposed in our gossip blog. The secrets are mainly there to keep the group entertaining and fun and for us to have a gossip blog that doesn’t focus on tearing people down. We want this place to be a safe place for our members and a place to have fun and develop your muse in your own way and your own time.
